{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":120,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_tan_wen_qi","speaker_name":"檀文琪","listener":"char_zhan_fei","text":"我们的赌注，以明日正午为期，那时裴珏与'冷谷双木'无论谁胜谁负，都必定已可分出结果，是么？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":32,"line_start":6,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_tan_wen_qi","text":"想必如此！","tone":"慌张","chapter":32,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_tan_wen_qi","speaker_name":"檀文琪","listener":"char_zhan_fei","text":"那时裴珏若已回转，我立刻便摘下我的眼睛，双手奉送到你面前；否则的话，我不说你也知道。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":32,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":null,"text":"其实姑娘又何苦与在下来赌眼睛？在下的这双眼睛，算不了什么；但裴大先生若是胜了，姑娘的这一双剪水秋波，血淋淋地挖将出来，却当真叫在下看了不忍！嘿嘿——各位，你说是么？","tone":"调侃","chapter":32,"line_start":42,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_tan_wen_qi","speaker_name":"檀文琪","listener":"char_zhan_fei","text":"是么……","tone":"冷酷","chapter":32,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_tan_wen_qi","speaker_name":"檀文琪","listener":null,"text":"裴珏若是胜了，我不但挖出眼睛，还要割下舌头，因为我再也不愿见到他，再也不愿与他说话……","tone":"激动","chapter":32,"line_start":52,"line_end":53},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"无名者","listener":null,"text":"裴……裴……","tone":"惊讶","chapter":32,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"群豪","listener":null,"text":"裴大先生！","tone":"激动","chapter":32,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_tan_ming","speaker_name":"檀明","listener":"char_tan_wen_qi","text":"琪儿！","tone":"焦急","chapter":32,"line_start":107,"line_end":107},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_tan_ming","text":"方才的赌注，可不是兄弟提出来的，檀老镖头休要忘了！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":32,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_tan_ming","speaker_name":"檀明","listener":"char_zhan_fei","text":"你说什么？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":32,"line_start":118,"line_end":118}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":121,"line_end":220,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_tan_ming","text":"难道仁义为先的檀大英雄，也不怕江湖中的耻笑？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":32,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"裴兄，有些人当真是有眼无珠，竟不信兄台会胜得'冷谷双木'……","tone":"调侃","chapter":32,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"谁说我胜了？","tone":"淡然","chapter":32,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"裴兄难道败了么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":32,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"谁说我败了？","tone":"淡然","chapter":32,"line_start":139,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":null,"text":"各位静一静好不好！","tone":"焦急","chapter":32,"line_start":148,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"裴兄，你到底是胜了，抑是败了？","tone":"无奈","chapter":32,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"胜了，胜了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"败了，败了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"胜了，败了……","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"五月的天气，的确是迷人的！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"在这里动手，两位可算得满意么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":null,"text":"此处大佳！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":182,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"那么两位此刻已可动手了！","tone":"微笑","chapter":32,"line_start":184,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"好好……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":32,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"老二，你先去领教。","tone":"淡然","chapter":32,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"我去么？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":32,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"自然是你去。","tone":"淡然","chapter":32,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":null,"text":"好，好，我去，我去！","tone":"无奈","chapter":32,"line_start":200,"line_end":200},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"请！","tone":"微笑","chapter":32,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你怎地不先出手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":32,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"在下并无与两位动手之意，而是两位向在下挑战的，自然先应让阁下出手才是。","tone":"微笑","chapter":32,"line_start":212,"line_end":214}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":221,"line_end":329,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你怎地不还手？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":32,"line_start":228,"line_end":228},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"我这不是还手？","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"你若要报那无端受辱之仇，你自己去动手好了！我……我疲倦得很……气力不济了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":32,"line_start":236,"line_end":237},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":null,"text":"好，好，我去，我去！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"不卷袖子，也一样可以动手的。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":32,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"不行，不行，我兄弟宁愿将'浪莽山庄'中的人全都杀死，也不愿碰你这种不会武的人一下。老二你说是嘛？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":32,"line_start":254,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"不错，不错！","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_leng_han_zhu","text":"但'冷谷双木'一世称雄，也不能无端被人欺侮，师傅找不到找徒弟，正是天经地义之事，老二，你说是吗？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":32,"line_start":262,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"不错，不错……那么怎么办呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":32,"line_start":266,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你虽然不会武功，但别的事你总会的吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":32,"line_start":270,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"那么你随意说出一件可以比试的东西来，无论是琴棋书画，文武两道，什么都可以。","tone":"陈述","chapter":32,"line_start":274,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"不瞒两位，在下一生之中，实在……实在……","tone":"悲伤","chapter":32,"line_start":293,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你难道什么都不会么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":32,"line_start":296,"line_end":296}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_tan_wen_qi","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":32,"line_start":52,"line_end":53,"text":"裴珏若是胜了，我不但挖出眼睛，还要割下舌头，因为我再也不愿见到他"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_pei_jue","type":"恋人","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"深情流露，因误会而决绝"}]},{"id":"char_leng_ku_mu","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["冷僻","固执","正义感强","重承诺","外冷内热","怜悯弱者"]},"source_refs":[{"chapter":32,"line_start":254,"line_end":256,"text":"我兄弟宁愿将'浪莽山庄'中的人全都杀死，也不愿碰你这种不会武的人一下"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_pei_jue","type":"对手","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"从敌意转为怜悯，不忍伤害"}]},{"id":"char_leng_han_zhu","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["冷僻","优柔寡断","重兄弟情","外冷内热","同情弱者"]},"source_refs":[{"chapter":32,"line_start":236,"line_end":237,"text":"你若要报那无端受辱之仇，你自己去动手好了！我……我疲倦得很……气力不济了。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_pei_jue","type":"对手","intensity":25,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"不愿伤害不会武功之人"}]}]}
